author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Plumbing sound reduction tips…running water can be loud, plus it’s nice to have privacy in bathrooms. I’m using Safe’n’Sound in this plumbing wall to solve both those problems. I use a mineral wool knife to cut it. And it’s easy to fit behind or between pipes. Many thanks to Rockwool for sending materials for my client’s bathroom project 🔥#sounddeadening #insulation #rockwoolinsulation #homerepairtutor #brandpartner
title: Plumbing Sound Reduction Tips - #shorts #rockwoolinsulation #brandpartner
